{"type": "article", "id": 4377, "title": "Ruban 开瓶器", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-15T07:55:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233051ibZNUfsegYVmqv5y.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国设计师 José Cabrita 日前带来一款名为「Ruban」的开瓶器，从其名大概可以看出，设计师是想借用这款极简主义造型的开瓶器向春秋末年的中国著名工匠鲁班致敬吧。越简单的产品越难做，而这款不锈钢材质的开瓶器，则将简洁做出了美感，开瓶的部位因其功能性被做成了折起来的书页模样。此外，José Cabrita 还非常注重对于细节的处理，将正面进行抛光，做出如镜面一般的效果，而背面则保留了磨砂质感。定价 55 欧元，<a href=\"http://contexte.bigcartel.com/product/ruban\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233050V9WlMtNnYJ0emx1u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233050nXmvWg2lNxqCKO8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.534375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330509oQpgsTAF8enhylN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"http://www.shejipi.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/349a5c9bc187d488d098304a79d70c952.gif\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}